documents.title: pgvector
documents.content: pgvector is a PostgreSQL extension that provides support for vector similarity search and nearest neighbor search in SQL.

documents.title: pg_similarity
documents.content: pg_similarity is a PostgreSQL extension that provides similarity and distance operators for vector columns.

documents.title: pg_trgm
documents.content: pg_trgm is a PostgreSQL extension that provides functions and operators for determining the similarity of alphanumeric text based on trigram matching.

documents.title: pg_prewarm
documents.content: pg_prewarm is a PostgreSQL extension that provides functions for prewarming relation data into the PostgreSQL buffer cache.
